s leveraging our approach match existing shared autonomy\nmethods for known goals, and outperform imitation learning baselines on new\ntasks. See videos here: https://youtu.be/Plh4t3wQeIA\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jul 2021 17:34:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Sep 2021 15:41:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-29"}
