en these two\nparameters is obtained and used as a guideline to select the optimum penalty\nterms in a Navier-Stokes solver, to simulate flow past a cylinder.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Jul 2021 15:32:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-09"}
